Title.English: PSG vs  Flamengo - FIFA Intercontinental Cup Qatar 2025 - Mini Match
Title.Arabic: PSG vs  Flamengo - FIFA Intercontinental Cup Qatar 2025 - Mini Match

Remarks.English:
Champions of Europe meet the champions of South America for the right to be crowned FIFA Intercontinental Cup winners.
PSG won their first ever UEFA Champions League title in May 2025.
Flamengo won the Copa Libertadores, in November 2025, for the fourth time in their history.
Victory for PSG will see them win their sixth trophy of the year, Flamengo could win an amazing fifth trophy in the last 19 days.
The match is live from Ahmed bin Ali Stadium, Doha, Qatar
